@startuml
title Purchase Portal - Submit Order Flow

actor Parent
... AI Chatbot suggests order tracking ...
participant Portal
participant Vendor
participant SendGrid

Parent -> Portal: Submit Order
Portal -> Vendor: Notify vendor of new order
Vendor --> Portal: Confirm acceptance
Portal -> SendGrid: Send confirmation email
SendGrid --> Parent: Email sent

alt Vendor Rejects Order
    Vendor --> Portal: Reject reason
    Portal --> Parent: Display error message
else Vendor Accepts Order
    Portal -> Parent: Show “Order Approved”
end

Portal <-- Parent: Acknowledgement
@enduml
